{
  "texts": [
    "This personalized support facilitates the learner's progression through their ZPD, enabling them to achieve a higher level of understanding and skill.",
    "These are the foundational levels of PL.",
    "Moving up the higher levels of PL requires a sophisticated understanding of individual learners' cognitive and emotional states, as well as the ability to dynamically adjust teaching strategies.",
    "Advanced levels of personalized learning (PL) involve modeling the learner and maintaining a dynamic profile that encompasses their knowledge, skills, preferences, and learning behaviors.",
    "Within the context of the Zone of Proximal Development (ZPD), such a model would help identify the learner's current level of development and their potential for growth with assistance, enabling more effective scaffolding tailored to their needs (Comstock, 2024; Laak & Aru, 2024)."
  ]
}